        </div>
        <div class="contact-item" onclick="window.location.href='tel:+201000000000'">
          <div class="contact-icon" style="background:var(--mint)">📱</div>
          <div><div class="contact-label">WhatsApp</div><div class="contact-value">+20 100 000 0000</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-item">
          <div class="contact-icon" style="background:var(--peach)">⏰</div>
          <div><div class="contact-label">Working Hours</div><div class="contact-value">Sun–Thu · 9AM–6PM (Cairo time)</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div class="faq-card">
        <div class="faq-card-header"><h3>❓ Frequently Asked</h3></div>
        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          <div class="faq-question">Is BridgeUp free to use? <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></div>
          <div class="faq-answer">Most of our courses and features are completely free. Some premium courses and therapy sessions are paid, but we'll always show you the price clearly before you commit.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          <div class="faq-question">Are the therapists certified? <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></div>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yes. All therapists and coaches on BridgeUp are verified and certified by the Egyptian Ministry of Health or equivalent bodies. We review credentials before onboarding anyone.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          <div class="faq-question">Can I cancel a booking? <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></div>
          <div class="faq-answer">You can cancel a session up to 24 hours before it starts at no charge. Cancellations within 24 hours may incur a partial fee depending on the provider's policy.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          <div class="faq-question">Is my data safe? <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></div>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yes. All data is encrypted and stored securely. We never sell personal data. You can delete your account and all associated data at any time from your profile settings.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
          <div class="faq-question">What languages are supported? <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></div>
          <div class="faq-answer">BridgeUp is currently available in English and Arabic. French is coming soon. You can set your preferred language in your profile settings.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
